{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":763,"text":"You're looking at a woman\nwho was publicly silent for a decade."},{"time":6711,"text":"Obviously, that's changed,"},{"time":8967,"text":"but only recently."}]},{"cues":[{"time":11051,"text":"It was several months ago"},{"time":12629,"text":"that I gave my very first\nmajor public talk"},{"time":15602,"text":"at the Forbes 30 Under 30 summit:"},{"time":18217,"text":"1,500 brilliant people,\nall under the age of 30."},{"time":23101,"text":"That meant that in 1998,"},{"time":25865,"text":"the oldest among the group were only 14,"},{"time":29452,"text":"and the youngest, just four."},{"time":33039,"text":"I joked with them that some\nmight only have heard of me"},{"time":36628,"text":"from rap songs."},{"time":38580,"text":"Yes, I'm in rap songs."},{"time":41727,"text":"Almost 40 rap songs. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":46614,"text":"But the night of my speech,\na surprising thing happened."},{"time":50109,"text":"At the age of 41, I was hit on\nby a 27-year-old guy."},{"time":57155,"text":"I know, right?"},{"time":60301,"text":"He was charming and I was flattered,"},{"time":62914,"text":"and I declined."},{"time":65387,"text":"You know what his\nunsuccessful pickup line was?"},{"time":69141,"text":"He could make me feel 22 again."},{"time":72461,"text":"(Laughter) (Applause)"},{"time":78637,"text":"I realized later that night,\nI'm probably the only person over 40"},{"time":83908,"text":"who does not want to be 22 again."},{"time":86509,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":89109,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":95269,"text":"At the age of 22,\nI fell in love with my boss,"},{"time":100294,"text":"and at the age of 24,"},{"time":103115,"text":"I learned the devastating consequences."}]},{"cues":[{"time":107667,"text":"Can I see a show of hands of anyone here"},{"time":110848,"text":"who didn't make a mistake\nor do something they regretted at 22?"},{"time":117151,"text":"Yep. That's what I thought."},{"time":120648,"text":"So like me, at 22, a few of you\nmay have also taken wrong turns"},{"time":126428,"text":"and fallen in love with the wrong person,"},{"time":129466,"text":"maybe even your boss."},{"time":132378,"text":"Unlike me, though, your boss"},{"time":134973,"text":"probably wasn't the president\nof the United States of America."},{"time":139802,"text":"Of course, life is full of surprises."}]},{"cues":[{"time":144098,"text":"Not a day goes by that I'm not\nreminded of my mistake,"},{"time":149021,"text":"and I regret that mistake deeply."}]},{"cues":[{"time":153404,"text":"In 1998, after having been swept up\ninto an improbable romance,"},{"time":160026,"text":"I was then swept up into the eye\nof a political, legal and media maelstrom"},{"time":165488,"text":"like we had never seen before."},{"time":169535,"text":"Remember, just a few years earlier,"},{"time":171877,"text":"news was consumed from just three places:"},{"time":174879,"text":"reading a newspaper or magazine,"},{"time":177551,"text":"listening to the radio,"},{"time":179386,"text":"or watching television."},{"time":181004,"text":"That was it."},{"time":182304,"text":"But that wasn't my fate."},{"time":186259,"text":"Instead, this scandal was brought to you"},{"time":189881,"text":"by the digital revolution."},{"time":192281,"text":"That meant we could access\nall the information we wanted,"},{"time":195988,"text":"when we wanted it, anytime, anywhere,"},{"time":200283,"text":"and when the story broke in January 1998,"},{"time":204973,"text":"it broke online."},{"time":207759,"text":"It was the first time the traditional news"},{"time":210760,"text":"was usurped by the Internet\nfor a major news story,"},{"time":215283,"text":"a click that reverberated\naround the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":220484,"text":"What that meant for me personally"},{"time":222922,"text":"was that overnight I went\nfrom being a completely private figure"},{"time":228040,"text":"to a publicly humiliated one worldwide."},{"time":233487,"text":"I was patient zero\nof losing a personal reputation"},{"time":237782,"text":"on a global scale almost instantaneously."}]},{"cues":[{"time":243588,"text":"This rush to judgment,\nenabled by technology,"},{"time":245927,"text":"led to mobs of virtual stone-throwers."},{"time":250042,"text":"Granted, it was before social media,"},{"time":253101,"text":"but people could still comment online,"},{"time":256653,"text":"email stories, and, of course,\nemail cruel jokes."},{"time":262881,"text":"News sources plastered\nphotos of me all over"},{"time":265970,"text":"to sell newspapers, banner ads online,"},{"time":269754,"text":"and to keep people tuned to the TV."},{"time":273913,"text":"Do you recall a particular image of me,"},{"time":277462,"text":"say, wearing a beret?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":281224,"text":"Now, I admit I made mistakes,"},{"time":284219,"text":"especially wearing that beret."},{"time":288267,"text":"But the attention and judgment\nthat I received, not the story,"},{"time":292556,"text":"but that I personally received,\nwas unprecedented."},{"time":296920,"text":"I was branded as a tramp,"},{"time":300079,"text":"tart, slut, whore, bimbo,"},{"time":306627,"text":"and, of course, that woman."},{"time":310455,"text":"I was seen by many"},{"time":313220,"text":"but actually known by few."},{"time":316608,"text":"And I get it: it was easy to forget"},{"time":320186,"text":"that that woman was dimensional,"},{"time":322787,"text":"had a soul, and was once unbroken."}]},{"cues":[{"time":329505,"text":"When this happened to me 17 years ago,\nthere was no name for it."},{"time":334404,"text":"Now we call it cyberbullying\nand online harassment."},{"time":340421,"text":"Today, I want to share\nsome of my experience with you,"},{"time":343917,"text":"talk about how that experience has helped\nshape my cultural observations,"},{"time":348351,"text":"and how I hope my past experience\ncan lead to a change that results"},{"time":353203,"text":"in less suffering for others."}]},{"cues":[{"time":358221,"text":"In 1998, I lost my reputation\nand my dignity."},{"time":363494,"text":"I lost almost everything,"},{"time":366994,"text":"and I almost lost my life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":372905,"text":"Let me paint a picture for you."},{"time":377319,"text":"It is September of 1998."},{"time":380866,"text":"I'm sitting in a windowless office room"},{"time":383552,"text":"inside the Office\nof the Independent Counsel"},{"time":386616,"text":"underneath humming fluorescent lights."},{"time":391051,"text":"I'm listening to the sound of my voice,"},{"time":394882,"text":"my voice on surreptitiously\ntaped phone calls"},{"time":398620,"text":"that a supposed friend\nhad made the year before."},{"time":401756,"text":"I'm here because\nI've been legally required"},{"time":405331,"text":"to personally authenticate\nall 20 hours of taped conversation."},{"time":413194,"text":"For the past eight months,\nthe mysterious content of these tapes"},{"time":417181,"text":"has hung like the Sword\nof Damocles over my head."},{"time":421129,"text":"I mean, who can remember\nwhat they said a year ago?"},{"time":425215,"text":"Scared and mortified, I listen,"},{"time":431013,"text":"listen as I prattle on\nabout the flotsam and jetsam of the day;"},{"time":435555,"text":"listen as I confess my love\nfor the president,"},{"time":439426,"text":"and, of course, my heartbreak;"},{"time":442805,"text":"listen to my sometimes catty,\nsometimes churlish, sometimes silly self"},{"time":447623,"text":"being cruel, unforgiving, uncouth;"},{"time":453262,"text":"listen, deeply, deeply ashamed,"},{"time":456121,"text":"to the worst version of myself,"},{"time":458805,"text":"a self I don't even recognize."}]},{"cues":[{"time":464537,"text":"A few days later, the Starr Report\nis released to Congress,"},{"time":468659,"text":"and all of those tapes and transcripts,\nthose stolen words, form a part of it."},{"time":474790,"text":"That people can read the transcripts\nis horrific enough,"},{"time":478961,"text":"but a few weeks later,"},{"time":481708,"text":"the audio tapes are aired on TV,"},{"time":485005,"text":"and significant portions\nmade available online."},{"time":490661,"text":"The public humiliation was excruciating."},{"time":495245,"text":"Life was almost unbearable."}]},{"cues":[{"time":500938,"text":"This was not something that happened\nwith regularity back then in 1998,"},{"time":506054,"text":"and by this, I mean the stealing\nof people's private words, actions,"},{"time":511836,"text":"conversations or photos,"},{"time":514459,"text":"and then making them public --"},{"time":517038,"text":"public without consent,"},{"time":519475,"text":"public without context,"},{"time":521937,"text":"and public without compassion."}]},{"cues":[{"time":526091,"text":"Fast forward 12 years to 2010,"},{"time":529181,"text":"and now social media has been born."},{"time":533158,"text":"The landscape has sadly become much\nmore populated with instances like mine,"},{"time":538190,"text":"whether or not someone\nactually make a mistake,"},{"time":541208,"text":"and now it's for both public\nand private people."},{"time":546920,"text":"The consequences for some\nhave become dire, very dire."}]},{"cues":[{"time":553799,"text":"I was on the phone with my mom"},{"time":556347,"text":"in September of 2010,"},{"time":559064,"text":"and we were talking about the news"},{"time":560921,"text":"of a young college freshman\nfrom Rutgers University"},{"time":563713,"text":"named Tyler Clementi."},{"time":566656,"text":"Sweet, sensitive, creative Tyler"},{"time":569804,"text":"was secretly webcammed by his roommate"},{"time":572183,"text":"while being intimate with another man."},{"time":576826,"text":"When the online world\nlearned of this incident,"},{"time":579264,"text":"the ridicule and cyberbullying ignited."},{"time":584079,"text":"A few days later,"},{"time":585998,"text":"Tyler jumped from \nthe George Washington Bridge"},{"time":589714,"text":"to his death."},{"time":591247,"text":"He was 18."}]},{"cues":[{"time":595644,"text":"My mom was beside herself about\nwhat happened to Tyler and his family,"},{"time":600347,"text":"and she was gutted with pain"},{"time":602902,"text":"in a way that I just couldn't\nquite understand,"},{"time":606570,"text":"and then eventually I realized"},{"time":608940,"text":"she was reliving 1998,"},{"time":611921,"text":"reliving a time when she sat\nby my bed every night,"},{"time":618824,"text":"reliving a time when she made me shower\nwith the bathroom door open,"},{"time":624797,"text":"and reliving a time\nwhen both of my parents feared"},{"time":628907,"text":"that I would be humiliated to death,"},{"time":631857,"text":"literally."}]},{"cues":[{"time":636339,"text":"Today, too many parents"},{"time":639286,"text":"haven't had the chance to step in\nand rescue their loved ones."},{"time":642628,"text":"Too many have learned\nof their child's suffering and humiliation"},{"time":646809,"text":"after it was too late."},{"time":649944,"text":"Tyler's tragic, senseless death\nwas a turning point for me."},{"time":654541,"text":"It served to recontextualize\nmy experiences,"},{"time":658582,"text":"and I then began to look at the world\nof humiliation and bullying around me"},{"time":662877,"text":"and see something different."},{"time":666360,"text":"In 1998, we had no way of knowing\nwhere this brave new technology"},{"time":671584,"text":"called the Internet would take us."},{"time":674254,"text":"Since then, it has connected people\nin unimaginable ways,"},{"time":678462,"text":"joining lost siblings,"},{"time":680379,"text":"saving lives, launching revolutions,"},{"time":684450,"text":"but the darkness, cyberbullying,\nand slut-shaming that I experienced"},{"time":689300,"text":"had mushroomed."},{"time":693145,"text":"Every day online, people,\nespecially young people"},{"time":697845,"text":"who are not developmentally\nequipped to handle this,"},{"time":700772,"text":"are so abused and humiliated"},{"time":703304,"text":"that they can't imagine living\nto the next day,"},{"time":705996,"text":"and some, tragically, don't,"},{"time":709145,"text":"and there's nothing virtual about that."},{"time":713551,"text":"ChildLine, a U.K. nonprofit that's focused\non helping young people on various issues,"},{"time":719628,"text":"released a staggering statistic\nlate last year:"},{"time":723309,"text":"From 2012 to 2013,"},{"time":726930,"text":"there was an 87 percent increase"},{"time":730204,"text":"in calls and emails related\nto cyberbullying."},{"time":735080,"text":"A meta-analysis done\nout of the Netherlands"},{"time":737262,"text":"showed that for the first time,"},{"time":739257,"text":"cyberbullying was leading\nto suicidal ideations"},{"time":744299,"text":"more significantly than offline bullying."},{"time":748199,"text":"And you know what shocked me,\nalthough it shouldn't have,"},{"time":751960,"text":"was other research last year\nthat determined humiliation"},{"time":755897,"text":"was a more intensely felt emotion"},{"time":758895,"text":"than either happiness or even anger."}]},{"cues":[{"time":764305,"text":"Cruelty to others is nothing new,"},{"time":767490,"text":"but online, technologically\nenhanced shaming is amplified,"},{"time":773870,"text":"uncontained, and permanently accessible."},{"time":779187,"text":"The echo of embarrassment used to extend\nonly as far as your family, village,"},{"time":784877,"text":"school or community,"},{"time":787221,"text":"but now it's the online community too."},{"time":791099,"text":"Millions of people, often anonymously,"},{"time":793941,"text":"can stab you with their words,\nand that's a lot of pain,"},{"time":797934,"text":"and there are no perimeters\naround how many people"},{"time":801070,"text":"can publicly observe you"},{"time":803158,"text":"and put you in a public stockade."},{"time":807717,"text":"There is a very personal price"},{"time":810186,"text":"to public humiliation,"},{"time":813130,"text":"and the growth of the Internet\nhas jacked up that price."}]},{"cues":[{"time":819841,"text":"For nearly two decades now,"},{"time":822268,"text":"we have slowly been sowing the seeds\nof shame and public humiliation"},{"time":826386,"text":"in our cultural soil,\nboth on- and offline."},{"time":832207,"text":"Gossip websites, paparazzi,\nreality programming, politics,"},{"time":837105,"text":"news outlets and sometimes hackers\nall traffic in shame."},{"time":842941,"text":"It's led to desensitization\nand a permissive environment online"},{"time":847159,"text":"which lends itself to trolling,\ninvasion of privacy, and cyberbullying."},{"time":853521,"text":"This shift has created\nwhat Professor Nicolaus Mills calls"},{"time":857306,"text":"a culture of humiliation."},{"time":861090,"text":"Consider a few prominent examples\njust from the past six months alone."},{"time":866269,"text":"Snapchat, the service which is used\nmainly by younger generations"},{"time":871353,"text":"and claims that its messages\nonly have the lifespan"},{"time":874048,"text":"of a few seconds."},{"time":875751,"text":"You can imagine the range\nof content that that gets."},{"time":879161,"text":"A third-party app which Snapchatters\nuse to preserve the lifespan"},{"time":883294,"text":"of the messages was hacked,"},{"time":885988,"text":"and 100,000 personal conversations,\nphotos, and videos were leaked online"},{"time":892838,"text":"to now have a lifespan of forever."},{"time":897095,"text":"Jennifer Lawrence and several other actors\nhad their iCloud accounts hacked,"},{"time":901251,"text":"and private, intimate, nude photos\nwere plastered across the Internet"},{"time":905198,"text":"without their permission."},{"time":907080,"text":"One gossip website\nhad over five million hits"},{"time":911212,"text":"for this one story."},{"time":915027,"text":"And what about the Sony Pictures\ncyberhacking?"},{"time":918526,"text":"The documents which received\nthe most attention"},{"time":921523,"text":"were private emails that had\nmaximum public embarrassment value."}]},{"cues":[{"time":927559,"text":"But in this culture of humiliation,"},{"time":930809,"text":"there is another kind of price tag\nattached to public shaming."},{"time":935639,"text":"The price does not measure\nthe cost to the victim,"},{"time":938797,"text":"which Tyler and too many others,"},{"time":941050,"text":"notably women, minorities,"},{"time":943024,"text":"and members of the LGBTQ\ncommunity have paid,"},{"time":947202,"text":"but the price measures the profit\nof those who prey on them."},{"time":952868,"text":"This invasion of others is a raw material,"},{"time":956931,"text":"efficiently and ruthlessly mined,\npackaged and sold at a profit."},{"time":962921,"text":"A marketplace has emerged\nwhere public humiliation is a commodity"},{"time":968703,"text":"and shame is an industry."},{"time":972047,"text":"How is the money made?"},{"time":975739,"text":"Clicks."},{"time":977573,"text":"The more shame, the more clicks."},{"time":980104,"text":"The more clicks,\nthe more advertising dollars."},{"time":985428,"text":"We're in a dangerous cycle."},{"time":987633,"text":"The more we click on this kind of gossip,"},{"time":990558,"text":"the more numb we get\nto the human lives behind it,"},{"time":994279,"text":"and the more numb we get,\nthe more we click."},{"time":999735,"text":"All the while, someone is making money"},{"time":1002658,"text":"off of the back \nof someone else's suffering."},{"time":1006871,"text":"With every click, we make a choice."},{"time":1009674,"text":"The more we saturate our culture\nwith public shaming,"},{"time":1013086,"text":"the more accepted it is,"},{"time":1014945,"text":"the more we will see behavior\nlike cyberbullying,"},{"time":1018148,"text":"trolling, some forms of hacking,"},{"time":1020795,"text":"and online harassment."},{"time":1023721,"text":"Why? Because they all have\nhumiliation at their cores."},{"time":1031429,"text":"This behavior is a symptom\nof the culture we've created."},{"time":1035725,"text":"Just think about it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1039232,"text":"Changing behavior begins\nwith evolving beliefs."},{"time":1042644,"text":"We've seen that to be true\nwith racism, homophobia,"},{"time":1046150,"text":"and plenty of other biases,\ntoday and in the past."},{"time":1050910,"text":"As we've changed beliefs\nabout same-sex marriage,"},{"time":1054068,"text":"more people have been\noffered equal freedoms."},{"time":1058550,"text":"When we began valuing sustainability,"},{"time":1060733,"text":"more people began to recycle."},{"time":1063681,"text":"So as far as our culture\nof humiliation goes,"},{"time":1066956,"text":"what we need is a cultural revolution."},{"time":1070601,"text":"Public shaming\nas a blood sport has to stop,"},{"time":1074524,"text":"and it's time for an intervention\non the Internet and in our culture."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1079401,"text":"The shift begins with something simple,\nbut it's not easy."},{"time":1084137,"text":"We need to return to a long-held value\nof compassion -- compassion and empathy."},{"time":1090772,"text":"Online, we've got a compassion deficit,"},{"time":1093959,"text":"an empathy crisis."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1097091,"text":"Researcher Bren√© Brown said, and I quote,"},{"time":1100995,"text":"\"Shame can't survive empathy.\""},{"time":1104571,"text":"Shame cannot survive empathy."},{"time":1110515,"text":"I've seen some very dark days in my life,"},{"time":1114136,"text":"and it was the compassion and empathy\nfrom my family, friends, professionals,"},{"time":1120197,"text":"and sometimes even strangers\nthat saved me."},{"time":1125583,"text":"Even empathy from one person\ncan make a difference."},{"time":1130318,"text":"The theory of minority influence,"},{"time":1132991,"text":"proposed by social psychologist\nSerge Moscovici,"},{"time":1136195,"text":"says that even in small numbers,"},{"time":1138981,"text":"when there's consistency over time,"},{"time":1141233,"text":"change can happen."},{"time":1143834,"text":"In the online world,\nwe can foster minority influence"},{"time":1147061,"text":"by becoming upstanders."},{"time":1149488,"text":"To become an upstander means\ninstead of bystander apathy,"},{"time":1153214,"text":"we can post a positive comment for someone\nor report a bullying situation."},{"time":1158452,"text":"Trust me, compassionate comments\nhelp abate the negativity."},{"time":1163385,"text":"We can also counteract the culture\nby supporting organizations"},{"time":1167193,"text":"that deal with these kinds of issues,"},{"time":1169469,"text":"like the Tyler Clementi\nFoundation in the U.S.,"},{"time":1172277,"text":"In the U.K., there's Anti-Bullying Pro,"},{"time":1175088,"text":"and in Australia, there's Project Rockit."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1180350,"text":"We talk a lot about our right\nto freedom of expression,"},{"time":1186157,"text":"but we need to talk more about"},{"time":1188182,"text":"our responsibility\nto freedom of expression."},{"time":1191736,"text":"We all want to be heard,"},{"time":1194475,"text":"but let's acknowledge the difference\nbetween speaking up with intention"},{"time":1199258,"text":"and speaking up for attention."},{"time":1203684,"text":"The Internet is \nthe superhighway for the id,"},{"time":1207222,"text":"but online, showing empathy to others"},{"time":1210380,"text":"benefits us all and helps create\na safer and better world."},{"time":1215930,"text":"We need to communicate\nonline with compassion,"},{"time":1219134,"text":"consume news with compassion,"},{"time":1221595,"text":"and click with compassion."},{"time":1224289,"text":"Just imagine walking a mile\nin someone else's headline."},{"time":1231476,"text":"I'd like to end on a personal note."},{"time":1235561,"text":"In the past nine months,"},{"time":1237651,"text":"the question I've been \nasked the most is why."},{"time":1241175,"text":"Why now? Why was I \nsticking my head above the parapet?"},{"time":1245193,"text":"You can read between the lines\nin those questions,"},{"time":1247710,"text":"and the answer has nothing\nto do with politics."},{"time":1251559,"text":"The top note answer was and is\nbecause it's time:"},{"time":1257166,"text":"time to stop tip-toeing around my past;"},{"time":1259873,"text":"time to stop living a life of opprobrium;"},{"time":1263115,"text":"and time to take back my narrative."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1266349,"text":"It's also not just about saving myself."},{"time":1271194,"text":"Anyone who is suffering from shame\nand public humiliation"},{"time":1274607,"text":"needs to know one thing:"},{"time":1277394,"text":"You can survive it."},{"time":1280111,"text":"I know it's hard."},{"time":1282874,"text":"It may not be painless, quick or easy,"},{"time":1286505,"text":"but you can insist\non a different ending to your story."},{"time":1291181,"text":"Have compassion for yourself."},{"time":1294548,"text":"We all deserve compassion,"},{"time":1297636,"text":"and to live both online and off\nin a more compassionate world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1303835,"text":"Thank you for listening."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1306435,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}